reviewText: First thought movie didn't work, but later found out it was cd player
The cd case was blank but movie is awesome and in perfect shape.
Such a fun movie!  It will always be a classic favorite.  My boys love the cars and the characters they have come to love.  And that catchy catch phrase? Ka-Chow!
I wish the price was better.
My son loves this movie!  This full screen edition is perfect to watch on a DVD player.  We have another wide screen edition to play on TV.
